> Look around too for evidence of someplace that might have been
> attached. Wires develop a memory and like to hang near where they were
> detached from. Look for a screw it might have been attached to, with
> attendant wear signs where the connector might have been. Often I have
> found stray wires because a PO had some accessory they wanted a power
> wire for. Removed accessory and left stray wire.
